e and no direct reflection.\n\nSo I left the public-API coverage test in place, but I did not add an artificial internal invocation for the unreachable synthetic `class$` call site.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_01bc23ed220918b4016a27356ca99881968276fb926753de90\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 743, "output": 1830, "cacheRead": 36352, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 38925, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1780954410879, "responseId": "resp_01bc23ed220918b4016a27352b75d08196a613a7ea39a10504"}}
